description: Redevelopment of the site to deliver a 20 storey mixed use building comprising 105 residential units (13 x studios, 45 x 1 beds, 31 x 2 beds and 16 x 3 beds), 172 sq. m. (GEA) of flexible non-residential floorspace (Use Classes A1-A4 and B1) together with associated car and cycle parking and landscaping and associated works. This application affects the setting of two Grade II listed buildings. The listed buildings are nineteenth century industrial warehouses and are listed as Warehouse K and Warehouse W.
